<section id="fb1">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">changes: Not all changes over the period were increases.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb2">
  <p align="left">in</p>
</section>

<section id="fb3">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">had: The chart does not show present situation, so present perfect is not appropriate here.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb4">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">sharply: The adverb is needed here, to describe the verb 'decline'.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb5">
  <p align="left">million</p>
</section>

<section id="fb6">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">quarter: From 120,000 to 95,000.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb7">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">increased: Rise is an intransitive verb. It does not take an object.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb8">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">dramatic: The correct form of the adjective is 'dramatic'.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb9">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">which: The pronoun refers to the word 'membership', not to individuals.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb10">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">to: From 130,000 to 665,000.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb11">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">high: The structure is 'as + adjective + as'. The comparative form is not used.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb12">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">doubled: From 80,000 to 165,000.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb13">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">a proportion: In this case, the proportion is a percentage.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb14">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">over: 12% is just over 1 in 10.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb15">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">majority: 48% say that they practically never attend services, and 10% say they have no religion.</font>
  </p>
</section>

<section id="fb16">
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">under: 12% is just over 1 in 10.</font>
  </p>
</section>

